item_name: Giovanna Collection Women's 3-piece Oversized Shawl Collar Brocade & Silk Wool Skirt Suit
product_description: Prepare yourself for your next special event with this stunning 3-piece skirt suit from Giovanna Collection! The jacket is made with patterned brocade with metallic threads, with pleats on the waistline and 2 hidden snap buttons closure. The camisole is made in silk wool with a side zipper closure. The paneled flare skirt is made in silk wool fabric, side elastic, back zipper closure. The whole outfit is fully lined. Measurements taken from size 10: jacket length from center back = 22" - 23", camisole length = 22", skirt length = 34" - 35".
